### ⚠️ 变量配置区 (注意这里要用 管理员 Token)
@admin_token = 你的管理员Token贴在这里
@hotel_id = 待审核的酒店ID

### 1. 查看所有酒店列表 (包含 status=0 待审核的)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/hotels/admin/list
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 2. 审核拒绝 (测试)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/hotels/{{hotel_id}}/audit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": 2,
  "rejectReason": "图片不清晰，请重新上传"
}

### 3. 审核通过 (正式发布)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/hotels/{{hotel_id}}/audit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": 1,
  "rejectReason": ""
}